-- MOVES-FTI Consulting names Richard Baxter as senior managing director 
-- By Rama Venkat Raman in Bangalore
-- Mon Oct 06, 2014 04:34AM EDT
-- None



Oct 6 (Reuters) - Business advisory firm FTI Consulting Inc <FCN.N> said it named Richard Baxter as a senior managing director and head of indirect taxation in its European Tax Advisory practice.

Based in London, Baxter will counsel clients regarding commercial value-added tax solutions. [ID:nPncBR9T]